<plot>A documentary that recounts the history and spirit of The Guilds of the Orange County Performing Arts Center, a volunteer group committed to encouraging appreciation of the arts. This film makes you believe in the passion for arts as told by those who raise funds daily for one of the world's truly great art centers. A portion of the film focuses on Elizabeth Segerstrom, wife of OC patriarch, Henry T. Segerstrom, as she is honored for her outstanding contributions to The Center.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?562995</url></doc>
